---
import BaseLayout from '@/components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About BloxTier and its independent Roblox competitive data workflow." path="/about/">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="surface rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8">
      <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-mint">About</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-black text-white">Independent Roblox competitive tools</h1>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-base leading-8 text-white/72">
        <p>BloxTier tracks Roblox games where players need fast decisions: which style to use, which loadout to test, which code claims still need verification, and what to compare before a match.</p>
        <p>The site separates verified code status from editorial tier analysis. Early tier data is intentionally labeled so it can improve without pretending to be official patch data.</p>
        <p>BloxTier is not affiliated with Roblox, FIFA, Gamefam, or the developers of listed Roblox experiences.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
